data.text: @Tirrimas @tomandlorenzo They adore each other and it shows. That's what so refreshing about these two. Fashion faux-pas? Who cares? More of them adoring each other please. You can be royalty and in love, come on.

@tomandlorenzo Somehow I 100% missed she was pregnant.  So I didn’t care about the tag, I was like “Hey! That fit is weird on her belly and she’s put her hand there just so!” And then I saw your comment about expecting and figured out everyone knew. 🤦‍♀️ I’m dumb.
@tomandlorenzo the pic of Harry flirting with her on the tarmac is TOO PRECIOUS.

@tomandlorenzo The tag is one of those country of origin, care and content things that is required by law to be sewn into the garment, now usually on a seam way down, out of sight. On this full skirt, she probably didn’t even know it was there.
@tomandlorenzo Not gonna lie, I thought someone photoshopped that on. That's such an odd place for a tag to be when the dress was cut shorter. Someone should have seen it.
@tomandlorenzo Seriously,  Harry’s underwear was sticking out of his pants the other day and people shrugged it off.   Get over this too.  🧐
